document_data.History:
Adrian was only ten years old when his father died in the {{YearlinkName|1135}}, and so his mother named [[Adom Kimball]], King of [[Moray]], to serve as regent over Callidyrr. Adrian assumed the throne in the {{YearlinkName|1141}}, when he was sixteen.

In [[1148 DR|the seventh year of his reign]], agents of the [[Kraken Society]] began operating throughout the [[North]] and the [[Moonshaes]].{{Cite dragon/362/Grand History of the Realms: The Moonshaes|30}}

Adrian ruled for sixty-six years before he died of natural causes in the {{YearlinkName|1207}}.
